@apiKey = thesis-secret-key

### Create a user
POST http://localhost:8081/api/users
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "username": "alice7"
}

> {%client.global.set("userId", response.body.userId); %}

### Send telemetry point 1 (should be queued)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/telemetry
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "timestamp": "2026-02-26T08:00:00Z",
  "latitude": 48.2082,
  "longitude": 16.3738
}

> {% client.global.set("rideId", response.body.rideId); %}

